        "### 3. Op√©rations arithm√©tiques\n",
        "\n",
        "Python permet d'effectuer toutes les op√©rations math√©matiques classiques :\n",
        "\n",
        "| Op√©ration | Symbole | Exemple | R√©sultat |\n",
        "|-----------|---------|---------|----------|\n",
        "| Addition | `+` | `5 + 3` | `8` |\n",
        "| Soustraction | `-` | `5 - 3` | `2` |\n",
        "| Multiplication | `*` | `5 * 3` | `15` |\n",
        "| Division | `/` | `5 / 2` | `2.5` |\n",
        "| Division enti√®re | `//` | `5 // 2` | `2` |\n",
        "| Modulo (reste) | `%` | `5 % 2` | `1` |\n",
        "| Puissance | `**` | `5 ** 2` | `25` |"
      ]
    },
